{"tid":1589509,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"612上神枱嘅最後機會!","createTime":"2019-09-23T10:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T00:03:29.000Z","uid":44461,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7890916a69339371729b7ca945ccaeb9cb109676","tid":1589509,"uid":44461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:21:48.000Z","msg":"眾所尻知，612基金有兩大問題:<br />\n<br />\n1. 批錢慢，有7000萬以上嘅財政儲備但係淨係批得200萬<br />\n<br />\n2. 揀case做，已經唔止有一個義士表示搵唔到612嘅人幫手，而搵到幫手嘅時候如果你見罪名低都唔會幫手<br />\n<br />\n而今日最新嘅核彈，就係有人發現左612洗左200萬入面，竟然有20萬係批俾民陣616遊行租音響!!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於呢件事，612方面嘅解釋係因為個陣民陣無錢，612就幫手出20萬，再俾民陣幫612籌錢，而最後嘅結果係出左二十萬，籌左一千萬。<br />\n<br />\n老實講，呢獲612係百辭莫辯，因為612打晒開口牌講淨係幫義士，同埋支出得200萬嘅時候竟然有20萬去左民陣到。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBUT!!!!!!!!!!!有危必有機。<br />\n<br />\n老實講我一路都唔太鐘意一早籌定一大堆錢打官司，一來用不其所，分分鐘啲錢2021年先會開始大幅流動，到時革命係咩狀況根本無人知。二來籌錢打官司我一向都覺得比較消極，如果拎7000萬黎整火魔法又好，買電單車護甲都好，對呢家前線嘅幫助都大啲。<br />\n<br />\n但係!!!!!!!!!!!既然開左個壞先例俾民陣，就係612反cup嘅好時機。<br />\n<br />\n612可以轉型為和理非/文宣活動嘅資金來源，例如係我想搞winter on fire放映會又好，社區連儂牆又好，呢啲都需要錢。當我搞放映會，如果我可以同612申請大約一萬蚊，用黎租器材同埋租室內場地之類，然後同一時間係場入面放612嘅籌款箱，類似賣旗袋咁唔俾打開嘅。咁係呢個活動入面籌到嘅錢，就全部俾晒612，咁就同俾20萬民陣拎返1000萬嘅概念係一樣。<br />\n<br />\n如果係呢家活動白熱化嘅途中，612可以加快速度，起碼一個月之內批返兩三百萬俾地區文宣用，我相信612上神枱嘅日子指日可待。<br />\n<br />\n絕對唔洗擔心啲錢會洗晒，香港人最多嘅係錢，買贖罪劵嘅人多的是。<br />\n<br />\n來吧，612反cup的日子來到了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n延伸自討論:<br />\n<br />\n(喜訊）原來612基金真係會批錢畀活動！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589286\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589286</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8fce387b16a7b3eccf99a42e2a05b7cd08553ad1","tid":1589509,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:22:42.000Z","msg":"[緊急][公投][置頂] 10.1集合定分區搞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589182</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5180900b6d4247b185a41448572c330690f99a4e","tid":1589509,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:23:26.000Z","msg":"[一至五帶風向]教大家phone-in節目提高駁入直播室嘅成功率<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587823</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dc454a487bc38ab591e8d3dcbabef09c8c6229b